original_title: ハイパープロジェクション演劇えんげき「ハイキュー!!」"はじまりの巨人
overview: The fifth stage play adaption of Haruichi Furudate's Haikyū!! series. The stage play focused on Hinata and Kageyama developing their new attack, as well as portraying the stories of other members on the Karasuno team. It covered Karasuno's matches against Johzenji and Wakutani South during the Spring Interhigh preliminaries.
title: Hyper Projection Play "Haikyuu!!" The Start of the Giant
